org.restsql.core
Class Factory

java.lang.Object
  org.restsql.core.Factory

public class Factory
extends Object

Creates implemenations and also is a facade for other framework factories. Customize the framework with new factories that use custom API implementation classes. Use restsql properties to specify the implemenation class names.

Author:
Mark Sawers
